Robot will solve a maze.
Maze shall be defined by thick (~1 in.) lines on a light-colored tile floor. Tentative size of each "cell" in the maze is 12 sq. in.
 The "exit" shall be a piece of white paper (albedo > floor's).

The leJOS NXT API is available here: 
http://lejos.sourceforge.net/nxt/nxj/api/index.html


